data.description: Stunning 3-bedroom and 2.5-bath townhome with a spacious loft on the 3rd floor and tons of natural light! The first floor boasts luxury vinyl planking and an open concept layout, perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying quality time with family. Kitchen features quartz countertops, stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinet space. Large walk-in closet located in the primary bedroom and spacious additional rooms throughout. Spacious garage with additional ceiling storage racks. Step outside to the back patio and discover a wonderful covered area, ideal for enjoying the outdoors in any weather. Whether you desire a tranquil space to relax or an outdoor dining area, this patio has you covered. A perfect blend of comfort and style awaits in this impressive townhome. Don't miss out! Schedule a showing today.
